        <abstract>
            <p>Sorry to hear of JDH’s household troubles.</p> 
<p>Will try to get a couple of flowers of <hi rend="italic">Leschenaultia</hi> to send him.</p> 
            <p>"What a good case that of the Cameroons"; the 4000ft [elevation] is much to CD’s "private satisfaction".</p> 
<p>Sends JDH a copy of <hi rend="italic">Orchids</hi>.</p> 
